---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SideDrawer from '../components/SideDrawer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Command Structure | SPS" description="Meet the leadership behind India's premier security intelligence platform. Veterans from the NSG, Intelligence Bureau, and Corporate Risk Management.">
  <SideDrawer />

  <section class="brutalist-section pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="brutalist-container pl-20">
      <h1 class="text-heading-1 text-primary-accent mb-6">COMMAND STRUCTURE</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-3xl mb-16 leading-relaxed">
        We do not employ 'managers'. We deploy commanders. Our leadership is forged in the crucible of active duty—from the Black Cats of the NSG to the corridors of the Intelligence Bureau.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-20">
        
        <!-- Profile 1: The Founder & Sukhi Enterprise Heritage -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start border-b border-neutral-800 pb-20">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 relative group overflow-hidden">
               <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-800 font-black text-9xl select-none group-hover:text-neutral-700 transition-colors">
                 CMD
               </div>
               <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent w-full">
                 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">The Sukhi Family</h2>
                 <p class="text-primary-accent font-mono text-sm mt-1">FOUNDERS · EST. 1965</p>
               </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Sukhi Enterprise Heritage</h3>
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-neutral-400">
              <p>
                <strong>Sukhi Enterprise</strong> was founded in 1965 by a family with deep roots in security and protection services. What began as a small security agency in Mumbai has grown over six decades into one of India's most respected security intelligence organizations.
              </p>
              <p>
                The founding vision was simple but revolutionary: security is not about manning gates—it's about understanding threats before they materialize. This philosophy of <em>"Intelligence-First Security"</em> has guided every deployment, every training program, and every innovation at SPS.
              </p>
              <p>
                Today, the Sukhi Enterprise continues its legacy through SPS, now serving 10 critical sectors across India. The family's commitment to quality, integrity, and continuous improvement remains the cornerstone of our operations. Our guards don't just protect—they observe, report, and prevent.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 p-6 border border-primary-accent/30 bg-primary-accent/5">
              <blockquote class="text-xl text-neutral-300 italic">
                "A guard should see what others miss. That's the difference between security and intelligence."
              </blockquote>
              <p class="text-sm text-primary-accent mt-4 font-bold">— Sukhi Enterprise Founding Principle</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
              <div class="p-4 border border-neutral-800 text-center">
                <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-compliance mb-1">1965</span>
                <span class="block text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase">Established</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 border border-neutral-800 text-center">
                <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-success mb-1">60+</span>
                <span class="block text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase">Years Active</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 border border-neutral-800 text-center">
                <span class="block text-3xl font-bold text-primary-accent mb-1">10</span>
                <span class="block text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase">Sectors Served</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Profile 2: The Operator -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start border-b border-neutral-800 pb-20">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 relative group overflow-hidden">
               <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-800 font-black text-9xl select-none group-hover:text-neutral-700 transition-colors">
                 OPS
               </div>
               <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent w-full">
                 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Col. V.K. Singh (Retd.)</h2>
                 <p class="text-primary-accent font-mono text-sm mt-1">CHIEF OPERATIONS OFFICER</p>
               </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Tactician</h3>
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-neutral-400">
              <p>
                A veteran of the National Security Guard (NSG) - 51 SAG, Col. Singh specialises in counter-terror operations and hostage rescue. He brings the NSG's "Zero Error" culture to corporate security.
              </p>
              <p>
                At SPS, he oversees the 'Black Squad' – our elite QRT units deployed for high-risk asset protection. He personally designed the 'Manesar Corridor' protocol that kept supply lines open during the 2025 auto-sector strikes.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="p-4 border border-neutral-800">
                <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 uppercase">Service</span>
                <span class="block text-white font-mono">NSG (Black Cats) / Indian Army</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 border border-neutral-800">
                <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 uppercase">Specialisation</span>
                <span class="block text-white font-mono">Counter-Insurgency / Crisis Mgmt</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Profile 3: The Analyst -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-neutral-900 border border-neutral-800 relative group overflow-hidden">
               <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-800 font-black text-9xl select-none group-hover:text-neutral-700 transition-colors">
                 INT
               </div>
               <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent w-full">
                 <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Aditi Rao</h2>
                 <p class="text-primary-accent font-mono text-sm mt-1">HEAD OF INTELLIGENCE</p>
               </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Analyst</h3>
            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg text-neutral-400">
              <p>
                Ex-Intelligence Bureau (Technical Wing). Aditi Rao pivoted to the private sector to address the growing cyber-physical convergence gap. She leads the 'SPS Newsroom' and Threat Intelligence Cell.
              </p>
              <p>
                Her team was responsible for uncovering the 'Digital Arrest' scam patterns in Pune, saving clients over ₹4.5 Crores in 2025 alone. She authors the weekly 'Threat Vector' reports.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="p-4 border border-neutral-800">
                <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 uppercase">Background</span>
                <span class="block text-white font-mono">Intelligence Bureau (Tech)</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-4 border border-neutral-800">
                <span class="block text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 uppercase">Focus</span>
                <span class="block text-white font-mono">Cyber-Physical Convergence</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
